@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5568
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam BackgroundColor #FAFAFA

<style>
document {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  FontName "Segoe UI"
  FontColor #2D3748
}
activityDiagram {
  LineColor #4A5568
  LineThickness 1.5
  
  activity {
    RoundCorner 10
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    LineColor #CBD5E0
    FontColor #2D3748
    FontSize 11
    
    .siswa {
      BackgroundColor #EBF8FF
      LineColor #3182CE
      FontColor #2B6CB0
    }
    .petugas {
      BackgroundColor #FEFCBF
      LineColor #D69E2E
      FontColor #975A16
    }
    .admin {
      BackgroundColor #E6FFFA
      LineColor #319795
      FontColor #234E52
    }
    .success {
      BackgroundColor #C6F6D5
      LineColor #38A169
      FontColor #22543D
    }
    .fail {
      BackgroundColor #FED7D7
      LineColor #E53E3E
      FontColor #742A2A
    }
  }
  
  diamond {
    BackgroundColor #ED8936
    LineColor #DD6B20
    FontColor #FFFFFF
    FontSize 10
  }
  
  arrow {
    LineColor #4A5568
    LineThickness 1.5
  }
}
</style>

title Agile Scrum Development Method — Sistem Kantin Digital

skinparam swimlane {
  BorderColor #CBD5E0
  TitleBackgroundColor #F7FAFC
  TitleFontColor #2D3748
  TitleFontSize 12
  TitleFontWeight bold
}

|Product Owner|
start
:Membuat **Product Backlog**\n(Daftar semua fitur & prioritas); <<petugas>>

|Scrum Master + Team|
:**Sprint Planning**\n(Pilih fitur untuk sprint ini); <<siswa>>

:Membuat **Sprint Backlog**\n(Task breakdown 2 minggu); <<petugas>>

|Development Team|
repeat
  :**Sprint Cycle (2 Minggu)**\nCoding, Testing, Integration; <<admin>>

  :**Daily Standup (15 Menit)**\nProgress, Blocker, Plan; <<success>>

repeat while (Sprint belum selesai?) is (Lanjut)

:**Working App Increment**\n(Versi aplikasi yang berjalan); <<petugas>>

|Scrum Master + Team|
:**Sprint Review**\nDemo ke stakeholder; <<siswa>>

:**Sprint Retrospective**\nEvaluasi proses & perbaikan; <<siswa>>

|Product Owner|
if (Semua fitur selesai?) then (Ya)
  :**Release ke Production** 🚀; <<success>>
  stop
else (Belum)
  :Update Product Backlog\nberdasarkan feedback; <<petugas>>
  note right
    Feedback loop:
    Kembali ke Sprint Planning
  end note
  -> Iterasi berikutnya;
  |Scrum Master + Team|
  :**Sprint Planning**\n(Pilih fitur untuk sprint ini); <<siswa>>
  detach
endif

@enduml
